{"tid":1988042,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"有個傻鳩話Brent 期油冇可能負數，想害人？？？","createTime":"2020-04-25T02:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T22:13:12.000Z","uid":123335,"like":24,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"543c2e37adf0c42ad838c56de993086459733d7b","tid":1988042,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T02:24:27.000Z","msg":"<ins>Topic: </ins><br />\n入黎話你知紐約原油(WTI)及布蘭特原油既分別，<span style=\"color: red;\">同埋點解布蘭特期油唔會跌到負價</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1987215/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1987215/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>理論：</ins><br />\n為何布蘭特期油不會跌到負價？<br />\n紐約期油在早前跌至負數的原因是其合約只接受實物交割，若買家無法履行交割責任，只能以更低的價錢或倒貼其他買家接手其合約。而布蘭特期油則同時接受實物及現金結算，<span style=\"color: red;\">買家在期貨合約到期時可直接以現金結算，故其價錢在理論上不會跌至負數。</span><br />\n<br />\n佢IG: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/50am_investing/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F50am_investing%2F&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKseYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=371c68a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/50am_investing/</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n最簡單咪全世界庫存都滿晒<br />\n運輸同埋存倉嘅成本貴過石油本身<br />\n咪會搞到石油實物交割嘅價值變咗負數<br />\nEg -$50 <br />\n<br />\n你以為現金交割就冇事？<br />\n會唔會太天真？<br />\n油商會不斷沽期油黎對沖<br />\n大家都一齊掛淡倉沽落去<br />\n冇人會夠接膽接好倉 <br />\n然後，講下持好倉者，<br />\n當佢$2 買左，本身諗住撈底<br />\n見唔對路，心諗：「喂，啲油價奶晒嘢喎，好撚驚呀... 」<br />\n心理壓力太大，淆左底<br />\n但完全冇人Set $0 掛好倉<br />\n只有人掛左 $-0.5 掛好倉 <br />\n咁佢咪唯有用$-0.5 呢口價黎平倉 <br />\n然後咪會出現第一口既負油價<br />\nD人見到：「哇屌，原來Brent 期油都可以負數㗎？？？」<br />\n繼而再有恐慌性拋售，現金交割都可以預到去-$55<br />\n<br />\n機會細姐，唔代表冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主真係唔好害人啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己IQ唔夠<br />\n想像唔到<br />\n就話冇可能發生 <br />\nGoodest Logic <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：炒開期貨"},{"pid":"f10eaeedcc0131482be643a53e8ec32f433b8473","tid":1988042,"uid":36379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T02:24:36.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"9dfd0f7b028e49241ef7addd46e54e5dbced81eb","tid":1988042,"uid":113912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T02:24:52.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"6bef34dab27068af14c1264660360b1464803a0b","tid":1988042,"uid":43500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T02:25:15.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"b77311f0b2345d0685355d734afe80d896a8f0a8","tid":1988042,"uid":162558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T02:25:15.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"63504897b70c897b3c2ff935215a1b2432443271","tid":1988042,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T02:26:26.000Z","msg":"咁多bot <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b966911ae5151a7bea8534f6f6ca892088a7c0","tid":1988042,"uid":331631,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T02:27:15.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n上次WTI 跌負數之前啲人都係話「在理論上不會跌至負數」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />結果..."},{"pid":"a55e349fe6d6b6220f61774e4da098d283969f30","tid":1988042,"uid":50458,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T02:33:38.000Z","msg":"機會細都係有機會。<br />\n以為刀仔鋸大樹點知係刀仔輸身家。"},{"pid":"19e105dd02395bb1f51031d85e8fa1abadacec24","tid":1988042,"uid":293673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T02:35:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf9132625e4480479b5972e1632bc7ecb6307343","tid":1988042,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a55e349fe6d6b6220f61774e4da098d283969f30","tid":1988042,"uid":50458,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T02:33:38.000Z","msg":"機會細都係有機會。<br />\n以為刀仔鋸